_sText: I made this map with ideas zm_lila_panicdark gave me. There are many interactive props, such as Vending Machines, Couches, Radioactive Barrels, Explosive Barrels, and Oil Drums. Dynamic lighting is what gives this map the eerie effect of a deserted Psych. Ward! If DL Mirror doesnt work, you can DL from here http://files.gamebanana.com/maps/zm_bio_hazard.rar If you have any questions, you can reach me at...
